{"tid":1159038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[西環治港] 譚耀宗：王志民籲人大政協支持修訂逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-05-17T11:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T11:34:54.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6579ffb985a8729c93defe73423886ffc654fa4","tid":1159038,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348340&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkA2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=9616c822\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348340&h=3f30c2b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348340</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】全國人大常委譚耀宗在會後引述中聯辦主任王志民稱，中央支持修訂逃犯條例，呼籲人大政協支持，又指外國就修例可表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗：「為何中央不可發聲？他說有人指他一出聲就是干預，他說我們現在才說，其實先前已經，美國外國很多人說關於香港逃犯修訂條例，所以他們說就可以，中央發表意見就不可以？這是不可能的事。他表達了這個意見。至於立法會如何審議，他沒有具體說出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lUwEb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlUwEb.png&h=6f49e1e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c3836653e3d64f4d6b9fe51ee0cc472585e27f1","tid":1159038,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}